Market unfollow unfollow

Represents a market unfollow unfollow (in English: Volo Volo Market) is one of the most important shopping venues in the Comoros; It includes a lot of shops and stalls specializing in the sale of various products, goods, and crafts. [1]

Mount Karthala

Mount Karthala is (in English: Mount Karthala) the largest active volcano in the world; As Qatar reaches its crater to about 1.609 kilometers (one mile), which occurs volcanic eruptions between now and then, this has led to the latest explosions there is a huge cloud over the mountain dazzled both watched. [1]

Moheli Marine Park

Moheli Marine Park is located (English: The Moheli Marine Park) in Mwale Island (the smallest island in the Comoros), a breathtaking theme park was inserted as the first protected area in the State of the Comoros. [1]

Old Friday Mosque

There is the old (Friday Mosque in English: The Old Friday Mosque) in the island of Moroni, which is considered one of the important historical monuments in the country; Since the date of its construction dates back to the year one thousand four hundred and twenty-seven, this mosque features a great location, directly overlooking the Bay Harbor. [2]

Chumona Beach

There Chumona Beach (English: Beach of Chomoni) on the island of Grande Comore, a gorgeous beach features a scenic, golden sand soft, water with pure blue color, and perhaps the most characteristic of this beautiful beach is a volcanic rock, dark, black. [3 ]

Dragon appeared protrusion

[3]
